*
         * @prop {Array|undefined} value
         * @description
         *   Selected rows in the bulk action mode.

*
         * @prop {String} screenType
         * @description
         *   The screen type for the current screen (e.g. WebNotificationList) to get
         *   the correct permanent configuration schema.

*
         * @prop {String} routeContext
         * @description
         *   The route context from the current usage of the list.

*
         * @prop {String} specialItemListUrl
         * @description
         *   Holds the special item list url, if we need a different url as the local defined url.

*
         * @prop {String} listContext
         * @description
         *   Holds the list context, e.g. if you are comming from a detail view page.

*
         * @prop {Object} listConfig
         * @description
         *   The list config for the current list output.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} bulkMode
         * @description
         *   Disable the bulk action mode.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} disableAutoRefresh
         * @description
         *   Disables the automatic refresh of the list.

*
         * @prop {Object} additionalFetchItemListParams
         * @description
         *   A object of addtiioanl fetch item list params.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} prependedStaticColumns
         * @description
         *   A list of static (non-configurable) columns to be prepended to each row.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} appendedStaticColumns
         * @description
         *   A list of static (non-configurable) columns to be appended to each row.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} filterPresetsEnabled
         * @description
         *   Indicates if the filter presets feature is present.

*
         * @prop {undefined|Object} organizerItem
         * @description
         *   The organizer item in context.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} disableHighlightItem
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Disables the highlight item behaviour (on the first list load).

*
         * @prop {undefined|Number} highlightItemId
         * @description
         *   The item id to be highlighted. In the first load,
         *   if this prop isn't defined, the query param 'itemId'
         *   will be used.

*
         * @prop {undefined|Object} presetFilterRelation
         * @description
         *   The preset filter relation for the preset filter header and content.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} checkUserActivity
         * @description
         *   Indicates if the user activity should be checked.
This is needed to check, if the list config was really changed. Otherwise the newValue and oldValue is the
the same in the list config watcher.

             * @event input
             * @param {Array} newValue New selected bulk action items.
             * @description
             *   Raised when bulk action selection is changed.
